{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21027.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","nameNarration":"Chisato","narration":"After school that day,@Arisa called the other two over.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21027.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Arisa","nameRight":"Haruka","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"...So that's what's been going on."},{"chara":[{"id":403501}],"textRight":"Hmm, a picture book, you say?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"That sounds fun! I'll do it!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Chisato","textLeft":"Oh Matsuri, thank you!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Haruka","textRight":"Me too. If you need help, I'm here to lend@a hand!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Haruka, [chara:403401:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:403401:cheek_0][chara:403401:face_mtn_ex_011.exp.json][chara:403401:lipSynch_1]I won't forget this!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Arisa","textLeft":"So now that it's settled, let's start@brainstorming ideas."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":400}],"textRight":"Hold on a moment!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403301}],"textLeft":"What?"},{"chara":[{"id":403501,"motion":0}],"textRight":"We have plenty of time before the reading,@right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Chisato","textLeft":"Oh, yes. It's on the Sunday the week after@next."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403501}],"textRight":"Then we should take some time to work out@our ideas."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":1}],"textRight":"How about this?"},{"chara":[{"id":403501}],"textRight":"We'll all think of a base storyline@individually."},{"chara":[{"id":403501}],"textRight":"Then, in three days we'll present our ideas@to each other."},{"chara":[{"id":403501,"motion":100}],"textRight":"And from what we all have, we'll pick out@the building blocks for our actual story."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403501}],"textRight":"Our discussions will go faster if we have @a place to start from!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"I'm in!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Chisato","textLeft":"Yeah, you're right."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Arisa","textRight":"Okay! Then that's what we'll do!"},{"nameNarration":"Chisato","narration":"And so, we began making our picture book!","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21027.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_03"}],"nameCenter":"Chisato","textCenter":"*Sigh* I hope this ends well.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":403401}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}